  "title": "Tasty Charred Fluffy Wood Ear Mushroom Tagine",
  "description": "An energizing Moroccan dish featuring wood ear mushrooms that are charred and infused with aromatic spices for a delightful gluten-free breakfast or snack.",
  "cuisine": "Moroccan",
