  "instructions": [
    "Melt butter in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in tomato paste and spices. Cook for another minute.",
    "Fold in mushrooms and water; cover tightly with a lid.",
    "Cook for 10-12 minutes or until the mushrooms are charred on the outside and tender on the inside.",
    "Remove from heat, let sit for 5 minutes, then fluff mushrooms using a mortar and pestle.",
    "Serve warm."
